    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin. Can't wait to hear from you!",
