    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, and the transmission shifts effortlessly. The exterior retains a deep shine, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of tears, and all electronics\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. It has been garage-kept and comes with a full service history, recently receiving a fresh oil change and brake inspection. This is a reliable, turn-key car ready for its next owner.",
